    "body": "web3.js is not the culprit. There is actually no way to retrieve the revert reason from a node. [EIP 758](https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/blob/master/EIPS/eip-758.md) is a proposal to solve that, and there's Geth (https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/16424) and Ganache (https://github.com/trufflesuite/ganache-core/issues/116) issues to implement it.\r\n\r\nI guess we'll have to wait and see how that plays out.",
